Molecular Orbital (MO) Data:
---------------------------
  MO# i = ith MO in AIMAll (internal and output) order
  WMO#(i) = MO# i in wavefunction file order
  Occ_MO(i) = Occupancy of ith MO for Molecule
  Spin_MO(i) = Spin Type of ith MO
  Occ_MO(A,i) = Contribution of Atom A to Occ_MO(i)
  %Occ_MO(A,i) = 100 * Occ_MO(A,i) / Occ_MO(i)
  %N_MO(A,i) = 100 * Occ_MO(A,i) / N(A)
